In the MATTER OF the ESTATE OF Douglas CASTELLANO and the Parentage of Gregory Bock. (Estate of Douglas Castellano - Petitioner) C-699 September Term 2018
082132 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 21, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000165-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
